{"tid":369261,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"「摸5秒就捐45元！」奶襲哥爽埋30妹子乳溝狂甩","createTime":"2017-08-22T07:52:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-23T15:21:34.000Z","uid":8968,"like":7,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f4122c05626c665d77c387f6aeb32588c3cdcd81","tid":369261,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T07:52:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/22/154911_fd366ca487a33b7f9811c3355b2f0cda.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F22%2F154911_fd366ca487a33b7f9811c3355b2f0cda.jpg&h=e1cdcdb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一名自稱「搭訕大師」的男子，2個月前甫因在街頭以魔術為幌子，偷摸女生的胸部被警方拘留14天，被網友封為「奶襲哥」。想不到他又再出新招，假借公益為名，<span style=\"color: red;\">再次對30名女子搓揉胸部</span>得逞，引起網友撻伐，不過他卻不以為意，反嗆酸民沒本事，「<span style=\"color: red;\">說的好像你們能撩到一樣！</span>」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/22/154924_7741d63e1cedc79f12f1e38c0bf99eb9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F22%2F154924_7741d63e1cedc79f12f1e38c0bf99eb9.jpg&h=b1c430a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大陸網紅「Mr.柯李思」經常在《微博》上教授各種街頭搭訕技巧，日前他又想出了一個鬼點子，打著關心乳癌的口號，進行「摸胸挑戰」，在街頭隨機搭訕陌生女子<span style=\"color: red;\">，「讓我把頭埋妳胸裡5秒，只要挑戰成功，我們就會捐給中國紅十字會10塊錢（約台幣45元）。」</span>離譜的是，竟然還有30名女子答應接受挑戰，放任他將頭整個埋進乳溝狂甩；只有少數人覺得不對勁，笑著婉拒「你是想光明正大的揩油吧？」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/22/154944_454563ee9ae40a0b3519990a255fdc03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F22%2F154944_454563ee9ae40a0b3519990a255fdc03.jpg&h=e7a485dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然「奶襲哥」最後真的有將錢捐出去，但如此荒誕的「搭訕技巧」也引來兩派網友爭論，力挺他的粉絲看得嘖嘖稱奇，大讚神人、大師，甚至還要向他拜師，學習撩妹技；不過也有不少網友看了直搖頭，怒轟「女孩清醒點！都被這壞人占便宜！」、「套路太深，好多傻白甜」、「這些女生真的笨，自己的胸才值10元嗎？要做善事就直接做，搞這什麼名義測試？」<br />\n<br />\n面對抨擊，「奶襲哥」顯然沒在怕，反嗆那些罵他的網友「說的好像你們能撩到一樣！<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">吃不到葡萄說葡萄酸！</span>」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/NTdPP3PIZFg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNTdPP3PIZFg&d=X6Djyr7Uwvr%2FHWJcRpc4ZL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=e6b2523c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/NTdPP3PIZFg</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbfc68f1ea8bc673d1c54a5b0b57f9e9802698bd","tid":369261,"uid":69753,"like":8,"dislike":19,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T07:54:37.000Z","msg":"中國臭G倒貼都唔摸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7b6691f83fca45c50fc7af9e70c569e5a4d9733","tid":369261,"uid":5995,"like":5,"dislike":95,"score":-90,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T07:55:58.000Z","msg":"生得靚仔真係好"},{"pid":"49b7d4428c1add64bef20a472db0bef4423e89dd","tid":369261,"uid":8968,"like":7,"dislike":5,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T07:57:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中國臭G倒貼都唔摸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n酸到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f29fbd4a927b0244ecda48fff073fe3bfa56e04","tid":369261,"uid":8968,"like":169,"dislike":3,"score":166,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T07:57:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>生得靚仔真係好</blockquote><br />\n咁都靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1fa295138f11016dca1da816fb4512a9aaae600","tid":369261,"uid":13176,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T08:03:34.000Z","msg":"真係鬼國既人先諗得出同做得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"313417343b1a4968a256d3dd55f3b20fff0bcf20","tid":369261,"uid":8968,"like":23,"dislike":4,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T08:04:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真係鬼國既人先諗得出同做得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\